If you love pizza, we have two classes for you this weekend! Join us for Pizza on the Grill Demo at Lincoln Square on Sunday 8/29 at 11am. We also have a virtual Pizza Workshop on Sunday 8/28 at 1pm CST. Join us for both and get your fill of pizza! https://hubs.la/H0W22ws0
